element.name: Solitary Church of Souls by orangetigerprawn, Unknown Cache (2/1.5)

long-description.center:
Parish of St.Patrick, Church of the Immaculate Conception
on Balheary Avenue between Swords and Roganstown.
To find this arc you need to devine the answers the following mysteries

A: Number that rhymes with this hymn
Chapter 1

C: How many days in this creation
Chapter 3

D: Double the number of espressos
Chapter 4

E: How many lines of drones from Digitox were queuing to have new data inputted?
Chapter 5

element.encoded-hints: Thou my best thought, by day or by night, Waking or sleeping, Thy presence my light.

ul.li:
2010-05-01T19:00:00Z : Found it by abra123cadabra
Both Colorado and Cacheberry wouldn't settle on GZ. Enlightenment came with the hint. Nice spot.

2010-04-11T19:00:00Z : Found it by merann
Found fairly easily, nice spot. SL. TFTC, Merann.

2010-03-12T20:00:00Z : Found it by Fjon
Solved the puzzle while in work one day, and stopped off today - found very quickly.

2010-02-20T20:00:00Z : Found it by rooske
Don't know what number rhymes with hymn, so did't know number in first verse. I think there are 7 days in creation. Not a drop of coffee in sight. Have no imput into next line. But saying all that found cache within 1 minute, logged & left!! Happy days.

2010-02-14T20:00:00Z : Found it by Toffee Man
This was the last find on a nice day caching with Blue Jay 59. It was getting quite dark & we had to search for a while but we eventually found it. It was a nice way to spend Valentine's Day. TFTC Toffee Man #186
